text: Vitória importante na Liga das Nações. Obrigado pelo apoio de todos, vamos com tudo!

I've always dreamed of having my own watch collection. The Jacob & Co. Flight of CR7 & the Heart of CR7 takes inspiration from some of my most iconic moments on the field. I hope you like them as much as I do.
